headline: Should Investors Unfriend Meta Platforms Stock in 2025?
summary: Meta Platforms (NASDAQ: META) stock has dramatically improved over the last two years.  This move has fundamentally transformed the stock of Facebook's parent company.  Thus, investors should consider whether they want to foster this friendship with Meta, or if now is the time to unfriend the social media stock.

headline: The Heroic Race to Rescue 370 Orphans from a War Zone—Twice
